Package: stAirPol
Type: Package
Title: Spatio-temporal Modelling of Air Pollution Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Maxi Kellerbauer
Maintainer: Maxi Kellerbauer <maxi.kellerbauer@googlemail.com>
Description: Spatio-temporal Modelling of Air Pollution Data. This package takes the air pollution data from http://luftdaten.info, combines that data with metrological data from http://dwd.de, traffic informations from http://opentransportmap.info/ and informations about streets from https://openstreetmap.org and aggregates it to different time intervals. With that aggregated data it's possible to perform bayesian hierarchical spatio temporal modelling on it. The bayesian modelling is based on the `spTimer` package.
License: GPL-3
